SUMMARY:Trivia Night (Greensboro)
DESCRIPTION:Join NCWF Triad Wild! Chapter for a night of wildlife-themed trivia with some St. Patrick’s Day trivia sprinkled in! Come for a drink at The Loaded Grape\, and stay for rounds of fun trivia. Connect with like-minded people\, and learn how you can get involved with wildlife conservation\, education\, and habitat restoration here in Greensboro. There will be prizes for 1st and 2nd place winners in addition to a raffle fundraiser with great prizes after round 3. Join us for a fun evening! \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/trivia-night-greensboro/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/grape.jpg
END:VEVENT
