SUMMARY:Bear Pint Night (Asheville)
DESCRIPTION:Join Artemis Sportswomen\, NC Wildlife Federation\, and special guest North Carolina Wildlife Resources Commission Special Projects biologist Ashley Hobbs at Wicked Weed West for a BearWise presentation and Q&A session about bears and bear hunting regulations in western North Carolina. No registration required\, see you there! \nLEARN MORE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/bear-pint-night-asheville/
CATEGORIES:Featured
